{"text_id":85502,"tokens":["In"," this"," work",","," we"," present"," the"," preliminary"," results"," of"," our"," research"," into"," evolutionary"," mesh"," numbering","."," Our"," motivation"," for"," this"," study"," was"," to"," explore"," the"," potential"," benefits"," of"," using"," evolutionary"," algorithms"," to"," optimize"," mesh"," numbering"," processes"," in"," computational"," simulations","."," The"," numeric"," labels"," assigned"," to"," the"," nodes"," in"," a"," mesh"," provide"," critical"," input"," data"," for"," many"," simulations",","," and"," the"," quality"," of"," these"," labels"," can"," have"," a"," significant"," impact"," on"," their"," accuracy"," and"," performance","."," However",","," manual"," optimization"," of"," mesh"," numbering"," can"," be"," time","-","consuming",","," and"," traditional"," automated"," algorithms"," have"," limitations"," in"," addressing"," complex"," and"," variable"," meshes",".","To"," address"," this"," problem",","," we"," propose"," an"," evolutionary"," algorithm"," approach"," to"," mesh"," numbering"," that"," learns"," from"," and"," adapts"," to"," the"," mesh"," structure"," over"," time","."," Our"," methodology"," relies"," on"," the"," use"," of"," a"," genetic"," algorithm"," to"," evolve"," labeling"," schemes",","," with"," objective"," functions"," based"," on"," measures"," such"," as"," localization"," error"," and"," numerical"," stability","."," Our"," preliminary"," experiments"," on"," simple"," two","-","dimensional"," grids"," showed"," improved"," performance"," compared"," to"," standard"," mesh","-","of","-","sta","irc","ases"," numbering","."," We"," anticipate"," that"," this"," approach"," may"," be"," particularly"," useful"," for"," more"," complex"," mesh"," geometries"," encountered"," in"," practical"," simulation"," scenarios",".","In"," conclusion",","," this"," work"," contributes"," to"," the"," ongoing"," effort"," to"," develop"," more"," efficient"," and"," effective"," numerical"," methods"," for"," scientific"," and"," engineering"," simulation",","," and"," we"," look"," forward"," to"," further"," investigations"," on"," more"," complex"," meshes"," and"," higher","-","dimensional"," problems","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"gpt-3.5-turbo","label":1}